Stop following me.

00:22:32.940 --> 00:22:33.779
I'm going to ask Xiaowei myself.

00:22:33.779 --> 00:22:34.319
You can't go!

00:22:34.460 --> 00:22:35.000
Xiaofang!

00:22:36.119 --> 00:22:36.500
Xiaofang!

00:22:36.839 --> 00:22:37.339
Xiaowei!

00:22:37.880 --> 00:22:39.039
Why did you report me?

00:22:39.299 --> 00:22:40.940
Weren't we both willing?

00:22:41.319 --> 00:22:42.599
You said elope, we eloped.

00:22:42.599 --> 00:22:43.960
You said get married, we did.

00:22:44.160 --> 00:22:45.259
I did everything you said.

00:22:45.380 --> 00:22:46.539
Why did you go to the police station

00:22:46.539 --> 00:22:47.279
To report me?

00:22:48.339 --> 00:22:49.099
I didn't!

00:22:50.240 --> 00:22:51.519
Reporting him to the police?

00:22:52.059 --> 00:22:52.940
Qi Xiaowei,

00:22:53.119 --> 00:22:54.079
You dared drop your pants

00:22:54.079 --> 00:22:55.079
But won't own up to it, you coward!

00:22:55.500 --> 00:22:56.599
You call yourself a man?

00:22:58.380 --> 00:22:58.740
Auntie!

00:22:59.019 --> 00:22:59.500
Stop, that's enough!

00:22:59.500 --> 00:23:00.119
You're wasting your shoe.

00:23:00.440 --> 00:23:00.940
It's fine.

00:23:01.519 --> 00:23:02.279
One shoe's already thrown,

00:23:02.680 --> 00:23:03.339
The other's useless now anyway.

00:23:03.900 --> 00:23:04.660
Wha... what are you doing?

00:23:07.059 --> 00:23:07.740
Yang Fanmei!

00:23:07.900 --> 00:23:09.119
How dare you throw a shoe!

00:23:09.359 --> 00:23:10.180
You little shrew!

00:23:10.500 --> 00:23:11.519
Are... are you trying to kill someone?

00:23:11.559 --> 00:23:11.940
Yes.

00:23:13.400 --> 00:23:14.259
My sister,

00:23:15.279 --> 00:23:16.359
She might be a bit impulsive.

00:23:16.799 --> 00:23:18.460
But we're addressing the issue,

00:23:18.720 --> 00:23:19.359
Not attacking anyone.

00:23:19.960 --> 00:23:21.119
We should have

00:23:21.299 --> 00:23:22.359
A rational conversation.

00:23:22.519 --> 00:23:23.880
Rational my ass!

00:23:24.380 --> 00:23:25.059
You just want

00:23:25.059 --> 00:23:26.059
More money, don't you?

00:23:26.460 --> 00:23:27.240
Let me tell you,

00:23:27.579 --> 00:23:28.359
I'm not afraid.

00:23:29.119 --> 00:23:30.240
Go ahead and sue.

00:23:30.440 --> 00:23:30.960
Fine.

00:23:31.779 --> 00:23:33.480
Since you're saying

00:23:33.480 --> 00:23:34.359
Such irresponsible things,

00:23:34.880 --> 00:23:35.380
Then

00:23:35.740 --> 00:23:36.619
Xiaowei will just have to

00:23:37.140 --> 00:23:38.019
Go to prison.

00:23:38.500 --> 00:23:38.900
That's right.

00:23:39.220 --> 00:23:39.900
Do time.

00:23:41.359 --> 00:23:41.779
Let's go.

00:23:43.119 --> 00:23:43.579
Xiaowei!

00:23:43.900 --> 00:23:44.619
Come with me.

00:23:45.039 --> 00:23:46.259
Our business, we settle it ourselves.

00:23:47.819 --> 00:23:48.460
You're not going anywhere!

00:23:48.799 --> 00:23:49.799
You can't go, you're not allowed!

00:23:49.799 --> 00:23:50.500
You're not going anywhere!

00:23:50.819 --> 00:23:51.579
You're not going!

00:23:51.700 --> 00:23:52.099
You can't go!

00:23:52.099 --> 00:23:52.740
Talk right here.

00:23:52.740 --> 00:23:53.140
You can't go!

00:23:53.319 --> 00:23:53.640
Don't move!

00:23:54.240 --> 00:23:54.680
Talk right here.

00:23:55.099 --> 00:23:55.619
If you go with her,

00:23:55.619 --> 00:23:56.960
You'll get trapped again.

00:23:57.420 --> 00:23:59.099
Their family says one thing, does another.

00:23:59.099 --> 00:23:59.980
One plays good cop,

00:23:59.980 --> 00:24:00.740
The other plays bad cop.

00:24:01.000 --> 00:24:02.619
What if they really lock you up?

00:24:02.980 --> 00:24:03.400
You can't go!

00:24:07.339 --> 00:24:08.539
Qi Xiaowei, you don't trust me?

00:24:13.480 --> 00:24:13.960
You can't go.

00:24:18.339 --> 00:24:19.440
Qi Xiaowei!

00:24:20.619 --> 00:24:21.740
You coward!

00:24:22.380 --> 00:24:23.640
Just keep hiding in there!

00:24:24.400 --> 00:24:25.359
I'll get some dynamite

00:24:25.539 --> 00:24:26.559
And blow up your damn house!

00:24:29.099 --> 00:24:29.480
Don't move.

00:24:31.480 --> 00:24:32.359
I'm just gonna step out.

00:24:34.619 --> 00:24:35.359
Look how full of herself she is!

00:24:35.539 --> 00:24:37.259
Wants to blow us up with dynamite?

00:24:37.279 --> 00:24:37.839
Dynamite?

00:24:39.579 --> 00:24:40.019
Dad.

00:24:40.660 --> 00:24:42.279
Yang Fanmei's a real shrew.

00:24:42.359 --> 00:24:43.200
She'll do it if she says she will.

00:24:43.200 --> 00:24:44.700
Look what she did to my face!

00:24:45.000 --> 00:24:46.000
What are you yelling for?

00:24:46.539 --> 00:24:47.500
You think she's a firecracker

00:24:47.900 --> 00:24:48.700
That just blows up on command?

00:24:50.859 --> 00:24:52.000
Do you think Xiaowei might

00:24:52.019 --> 00:24:53.000
Actually get into legal trouble?

00:24:53.559 --> 00:24:54.279
What's there to be afraid of?

00:24:54.740 --> 00:24:55.339
Let her come.

00:24:55.759 --> 00:24:57.319
Let the storm rage even harder!

00:24:57.500 --> 00:24:58.259
Enough, you.

00:24:59.140 --> 00:25:00.140
What's wrong with you, kid?

00:25:00.480 --> 00:25:01.640
Such a shameful painting,

00:25:02.160 --> 00:25:03.099
Why did you go spreading it around?

00:25:03.740 --> 00:25:05.000
What? What did I spread?

00:25:06.160 --> 00:25:06.480
You...

00:25:07.619 --> 00:25:08.839
This. See for yourself.

00:25:17.640 --> 00:25:18.960
And I didn't say any of this.

00:25:19.839 --> 00:25:21.059
What was said doesn't matter.

00:25:21.519 --> 00:25:22.599
The point is this painting.

00:25:23.119 --> 00:25:23.900
Show him. Show him.

00:25:24.079 --> 00:25:25.000
The painting, right here, here.

00:25:27.099 --> 00:25:27.599
See it?

00:25:29.000 --> 00:25:29.720
You painted it, didn't you?

00:25:33.819 --> 00:25:34.099
This...

00:25:34.480 --> 00:25:35.740
Did you paint it, Xiaowei?

00:25:36.579 --> 00:25:37.380
Did you or didn't you?

00:25:38.640 --> 00:25:39.619
Say something!

00:25:40.200 --> 00:25:40.880
You definitely painted it.

00:25:49.500 --> 00:25:51.019
Did he paint it or not?

00:25:54.420 --> 00:25:56.359
Go, go, go, go!

00:25:56.799 --> 00:25:59.220
Go, go, go!

00:26:02.119 --> 00:26:02.700
Don't be a wimp!

00:26:03.000 --> 00:26:03.819
Nicely done!

00:26:03.980 --> 00:26:04.700
Hold on, hold on, hold on!

00:26:05.000 --> 00:26:05.460
Hold on!

00:26:07.380 --> 00:26:07.839
Get him!

00:26:07.940 --> 00:26:08.640
Get him! Get him!

00:26:09.500 --> 00:26:10.339
It's scared! It's scared!

00:26:12.160 --> 00:26:13.460
Didn't I sign up for installments?

00:26:13.460 --> 00:26:14.359
Why are you hounding me?

00:26:14.380 --> 00:26:15.000
Mr. Yang,

00:26:15.279 --> 00:26:16.880
Your installment was last month.

00:26:16.980 --> 00:26:18.420
Now you need to repay the principal.

00:26:18.539 --> 00:26:19.839
It's less than 50,000 yuan total.

00:26:19.900 --> 00:26:20.599
If you don't pay soon,

00:26:20.640 --> 00:26:21.980
It will affect your credit.

00:26:22.000 --> 00:26:22.740
Credit?

00:26:23.200 --> 00:26:23.960
My boss said

00:26:23.960 --> 00:26:24.779
He'd promote me and raise my pay.

00:26:24.779 --> 00:26:25.519
Did he follow through?

00:26:25.779 --> 00:26:26.640
Go find my boss,

00:26:27.059 --> 00:26:27.940
Tell him to keep his word

00:26:27.940 --> 00:26:28.759
And pay me my salary.

00:26:28.839 --> 00:26:30.240
Then I'll keep my word and pay you.

00:26:30.579 --> 00:26:30.900
Deal?

00:26:30.980 --> 00:26:32.480
I totally understand how you feel,

00:26:32.700 --> 00:26:33.779
But you still have to repay.

00:26:33.779 --> 00:26:34.299
Alright, alright.

00:26:34.299 --> 00:26:34.940
I get it, I get it.

00:26:35.240 --> 00:26:36.279
Go! Get him!

00:26:36.440 --> 00:26:37.900
Come on, fight, fight!

00:26:38.000 --> 00:26:39.200
50,000?

00:26:40.359 --> 00:26:41.700
You won't sell for 50,000?

00:26:43.099 --> 00:26:44.200
50,000 is way too little.

00:26:44.400 --> 00:26:45.640
My rooster has never lost.

00:26:45.819 --> 00:26:46.579
At least 80,000.

00:26:50.380 --> 00:26:51.400
Hey, hey, hey.

00:26:52.339 --> 00:26:53.140
How much for this rooster?

00:26:53.200 --> 00:26:53.539
80,000.

00:26:53.740 --> 00:26:54.519
That rooster?

00:26:54.880 --> 00:26:55.819
That rooster?

00:26:55.880 --> 00:26:56.220
Yeah.

00:26:56.980 --> 00:26:58.039
You wanna get into this, kid?

00:26:58.539 --> 00:26:59.160
Let's talk.

00:27:02.859 --> 00:27:04.539
I wish that rooster were mine.

00:27:06.240 --> 00:27:06.819
Fanzhu.

00:27:08.420 --> 00:27:08.880
Uncle.

00:27:09.380 --> 00:27:10.700
The college kid's back too!

00:27:10.920 --> 00:27:12.319
It's Mid-Autumn Festival, family reunion.

00:27:18.940 --> 00:27:20.460
You little brat, mocking me?

00:27:20.759 --> 00:27:21.819
My leg's gone numb.

00:27:22.259 --> 00:27:22.599
Okay.

00:27:23.980 --> 00:27:25.180
Why would I ever mock you?

00:27:29.420 --> 00:27:30.500
Fanzhu, Fanzhu.

00:27:30.759 --> 00:27:31.900
Wait up, wait up.

00:27:31.900 --> 00:27:32.859
Uncle, why are you chasing me?

00:27:32.859 --> 00:27:34.099
I really wasn't mocking you.

00:27:34.180 --> 00:27:35.400
That's not what I meant.

00:27:35.680 --> 00:27:37.740
I just looked for your brother; he wasn't home.

00:27:38.059 --> 00:27:39.279
Pass a message along for me.

00:27:39.500 --> 00:27:40.119
He loves eating this.

00:27:40.420 --> 00:27:41.099
Fresh out of the pot.

00:27:41.740 --> 00:27:44.019
So kind of you, you shouldn't have.

00:27:44.880 --> 00:27:45.980
Well, here's the thing.

00:27:46.740 --> 00:27:48.160
The town leaders assigned a task.

00:27:49.140 --> 00:27:50.079
Apparently, recently...

00:27:50.740 --> 00:27:53.119
A circus truck crashed near here.

00:27:53.480 --> 00:27:54.599
A monkey escaped.

00:27:54.960 --> 00:27:55.880
And it's their star performer.

00:27:56.319 --> 00:27:57.420
So they asked the villages below...

00:27:57.619 --> 00:27:58.460
To help look for it.

00:27:58.720 --> 00:27:59.599
The star performer's missing?

00:28:00.019 --> 00:28:01.079
There must be a big reward, right?

00:28:03.799 --> 00:28:05.460
Why is it always money with you?

00:28:05.880 --> 00:28:06.819
What does this have to do with money?

00:28:07.359 --> 00:28:08.740
This is a task from higher up.

00:28:09.480 --> 00:28:10.460
Let me tell you, young man,

00:28:10.720 --> 00:28:12.059
You gotta take the long view.

00:28:14.039 --> 00:28:15.480
Since when did you start making empty promises?

00:28:15.480 --> 00:28:16.599
Hard to swallow that.

00:28:18.839 --> 00:28:19.420
What do you mean?

00:28:21.660 --> 00:28:22.079
Don't get mad.

00:28:22.579 --> 00:28:23.660
Uncle, calm down, calm down. I...

00:28:24.339 --> 00:28:25.319
When my brother's free, I'll...

00:28:25.339 --> 00:28:25.859
Have him look for it.

00:28:26.119 --> 00:28:27.000
What do you mean "calm down"?

00:28:27.000 --> 00:28:27.640
What do you mean "when he's free"?

00:28:27.799 --> 00:28:28.740
By then that monkey will have run off...

00:28:28.740 --> 00:28:29.380
To another village.

00:28:30.319 --> 00:28:31.740
Then let the other villages find it.

00:28:32.579 --> 00:28:34.160
Whoever catches it gets a big reward.

00:28:38.420 --> 00:28:39.779
It's not a favor for nothing.

00:28:40.779 --> 00:28:41.839
Why didn't you say so sooner!

00:28:42.480 --> 00:28:42.960
Right away!

00:28:43.359 --> 00:28:44.019
Me and my brother, the two of us,

00:28:44.059 --> 00:28:44.980
Brothers joining forces,

00:28:45.279 --> 00:28:45.960
We'll go find it right away.

00:28:46.259 --> 00:28:46.759
Don't worry.

00:28:46.859 --> 00:28:47.859
When it comes to animals, we two

00:28:47.859 --> 00:28:49.099
Are like Sherlock Holmes and Watson.

00:28:49.359 --> 00:28:49.880
Three days.

00:28:50.359 --> 00:28:51.420
We'll definitely bring it back to you.

00:28:52.359 --> 00:28:52.759
Fanzhu.

00:28:53.460 --> 00:28:53.980
Let me tell you,

00:28:54.559 --> 00:28:55.859
You've been in the big city too long.

00:28:56.240 --> 00:28:57.240
You're obsessed with money.

00:28:58.740 --> 00:28:59.579
I'll say it one more time.

00:28:59.940 --> 00:29:00.980
Young folks need to take...

00:29:00.980 --> 00:29:01.859
The long view.

00:29:03.319 --> 00:29:04.420
Money, money, money.

00:29:04.579 --> 00:29:05.460
Like I don't want that money myself.

00:29:05.480 --> 00:29:06.500
Isn't your house the other way?

00:29:06.519 --> 00:29:07.460
Mind your own business.

00:29:10.380 --> 00:29:11.259
Being so secretive.

00:29:11.519 --> 00:29:12.539
Something's definitely fishy.

00:29:28.859 --> 00:29:29.519
Someone's there!

00:29:30.240 --> 00:29:30.680
No one's there.

00:29:33.119 --> 00:29:34.039
I'm telling you,

00:29:34.759 --> 00:29:35.700
Every time you come over,

00:29:36.119 --> 00:29:37.279
You're scared of this or that.

00:29:38.099 --> 00:29:38.720
What am I scared of?

00:29:39.140 --> 00:29:40.960
I'm a Militia Captain, what would I fear?

00:29:41.299 --> 00:29:42.480
Well, I'm the Women's Federation Director.

00:29:42.660 --> 00:29:43.220
What am I scared of?

00:29:48.440 --> 00:29:49.079
It's nothing.

00:29:50.059 --> 00:29:51.299
It was... a stray cat.

00:29:52.599 --> 00:29:54.220
What's scary about a stray cat?

00:29:54.559 --> 00:29:54.920
Right?

00:29:55.779 --> 00:29:57.240
Talking to you is exhausting.

00:29:58.519 --> 00:29:59.619
Yeah, you're the tough one.

00:29:59.680 --> 00:30:00.359
You're afraid of nothing.

00:30:00.940 --> 00:30:02.019
Afraid of nothing.

00:30:02.240 --> 00:30:02.859
Then why don't you dare

00:30:02.880 --> 00:30:04.279
Go public about us?

00:30:05.220 --> 00:30:06.619
It's not that I don't dare.

00:30:07.640 --> 00:30:08.319
I'm just waiting

00:30:08.339 --> 00:30:09.900
For the perfect moment.

00:30:10.539 --> 00:30:10.880
You know?

00:30:11.460 --> 00:30:12.859
If we don't handle this well,

00:30:13.059 --> 00:30:14.119
People will laugh at us.

00:30:14.500 --> 00:30:15.720
Who? Who's gonna laugh?

00:30:15.960 --> 00:30:16.859
Your wife passed away.

00:30:17.059 --> 00:30:17.960
My husband and I divorced.

00:30:18.240 --> 00:30:19.099
We're both single.

00:30:19.619 --> 00:30:20.420
Talking about marriage.

00:30:20.460 --> 00:30:21.859
Who's gonna laugh at us?

00:30:21.859 --> 00:30:22.500
Let's see who dares!

00:30:22.500 --> 00:30:24.240
No, no, no, stop, stop!

00:30:25.079 --> 00:30:25.779
Are you trying to suffocate me?

00:30:26.000 --> 00:30:26.740
Listen to me,

00:30:27.039 --> 00:30:28.539
You just don't get it.

00:30:29.119 --> 00:30:31.000
Look at Xiaofang and Xiaowei.

00:30:31.220 --> 00:30:32.519
Even they got laughed at.

00:30:33.859 --> 00:30:35.460
The rumors were awful.

00:30:35.740 --> 00:30:36.839
And they're young.

00:30:37.119 --> 00:30:38.359
They stepped out of line,

00:30:38.539 --> 00:30:40.319
And end up being talked about behind your back.

00:30:40.559 --> 00:30:41.640
Let alone us.

00:30:42.539 --> 00:30:43.000
Right?

00:30:43.180 --> 00:30:43.619
Well...

00:30:45.660 --> 00:30:46.500
You'd better tell me straight,

00:30:46.700 --> 00:30:47.599
What exactly are we?

00:30:48.079 --> 00:30:48.539
If you don't say it clearly,

00:30:48.539 --> 00:30:49.359
You're not leaving today.

00:30:50.880 --> 00:30:51.440
The two of us...

00:30:52.240 --> 00:30:52.960
We're just...

00:30:54.779 --> 00:30:55.960
You know, those two words.

00:30:56.400 --> 00:30:57.259
What two words?

00:30:57.920 --> 00:30:58.640
A secret affair!

00:30:59.779 --> 00:31:01.059
Are you trying to choke me?

00:31:03.779 --> 00:31:04.880
It's just those two words.

00:31:06.359 --> 00:31:07.339
What two words?

00:31:09.619 --> 00:31:10.440
Love...

00:31:14.119 --> 00:31:14.480
You.

00:31:15.819 --> 00:31:16.720
You wimp!

00:31:17.319 --> 00:31:18.920
Just like Xiaowei, no guts.

00:31:26.720 --> 00:31:27.279
Qi Xiaowei!

00:31:32.460 --> 00:31:33.619
Stop right there!

00:31:39.640 --> 00:31:40.539
Don't want to see me?

00:31:43.359 --> 00:31:45.319
This garbage stinks so bad.

00:31:46.099 --> 00:31:49.099
It's making me dizzy and deaf.

00:31:49.259 --> 00:31:50.400
The moment I heard your voice,

00:31:50.400 --> 00:31:51.220
Didn't I stop right away?

00:31:52.119 --> 00:31:53.099
So you're deaf during the day too?

00:31:54.680 --> 00:31:55.380
You don't trust me?

00:31:55.500 --> 00:31:56.019
I do.

00:31:56.440 --> 00:31:58.000
I trust you. Why wouldn't I?

00:32:02.720 --> 00:32:03.259
So spill it.

00:32:03.319 --> 00:32:04.480
What's the deal with that nude painting?

00:32:05.759 --> 00:32:07.339
I really didn't do it, honey.

00:32:07.500 --> 00:32:08.279
You're my wife.

00:32:08.279 --> 00:32:09.579
I would never do something like that.

00:32:09.759 --> 00:32:10.579
It really wasn't me.

00:32:10.980 --> 00:32:12.339
I know it wasn't you.

00:32:12.339 --> 00:32:13.700
We didn't finish it last time.

00:32:13.779 --> 00:32:14.359
So where did

00:32:14.380 --> 00:32:15.700
That nude painting come from?

00:32:19.500 --> 00:32:20.200
Well, with painting,

00:32:21.799 --> 00:32:24.619
You don't necessarily

00:32:25.140 --> 00:32:26.140
Need the model right in front of you.

00:32:27.059 --> 00:32:28.920
I went home

00:32:29.319 --> 00:32:30.440
And painted it from memory.

00:32:31.920 --> 00:32:33.279
It's you as I picture you.

00:32:34.940 --> 00:32:36.079
You really painted it?

00:32:40.039 --> 00:32:40.440
Well,

00:32:41.200 --> 00:32:43.000
Didn't I promise to paint one for you?

00:32:47.000 --> 00:32:47.859
You still remember?

00:32:48.380 --> 00:32:49.180
I thought you'd forgotten.

00:32:49.640 --> 00:32:50.039
I didn't.

00:32:53.220 --> 00:32:54.019
Then someone

00:32:54.019 --> 00:32:55.000
Secretly photographed the painting.

00:32:57.000 --> 00:32:57.799
How despicable!

00:32:57.799 --> 00:32:58.740
I'm gonna hunt them down!

00:32:59.240 --> 00:32:59.799
Honey, honey.

00:33:00.460 --> 00:33:01.119
Hold on, hold on.

00:33:04.000 --> 00:33:05.059
Calm down, calm down.

00:33:05.059 --> 00:33:05.740
It's late at night.

00:33:06.279 --> 00:33:07.839
Getting angry could harm the baby.

00:33:08.500 --> 00:33:09.359
Come on, I'll walk you home.

00:33:12.319 --> 00:33:13.180
Slow down, slow down, honey.

00:33:14.319 --> 00:33:14.859
Be careful.

00:33:15.240 --> 00:33:16.339
When did you paint it?

00:33:36.700 --> 00:33:37.480
Deaf?

00:33:38.539 --> 00:33:39.539
You're driving me crazy today!

00:33:46.559 --> 00:33:47.720
This painting must have been

00:33:47.720 --> 00:33:48.819
Secretly taken by someone close to you.

00:33:49.279 --> 00:33:50.200
You can't go soft on them.

00:33:50.220 --> 00:33:51.079
You've gotta teach him a lesson.

00:33:53.000 --> 00:33:53.839
I'll definitely find him.

00:33:54.279 --> 00:33:54.859
And teach him a real lesson.

00:34:14.199 --> 00:34:15.579
Even if we can't blow up their house,

00:34:16.179 --> 00:34:17.500
We've still gotta find a way

00:34:17.719 --> 00:34:18.460
To get that nude...

00:34:19.239 --> 00:34:20.480
That painting back.

00:34:21.840 --> 00:34:22.960
Of course we've gotta get it back.

00:34:23.360 --> 00:34:24.360
If it just sits there on display,

00:34:27.280 --> 00:34:28.719
You think the folks in our village

00:34:30.239 --> 00:34:32.219
Would settle for just looking at phones?

00:34:33.780 --> 00:34:34.360
That painting

00:34:34.599 --> 00:34:35.519
Is right by the entrance.

00:34:36.059 --> 00:34:37.739
Anyone walking in will see it.

00:34:39.000 --> 00:34:40.039
If it just stayed there,

00:34:40.039 --> 00:34:40.860
That'd actually be fine.

00:34:41.519 --> 00:34:42.199
You don't know, do you?

00:34:42.539 --> 00:34:44.480
Qi Xiaowei's holding an art show in the county.

00:34:44.820 --> 00:34:45.360
What?

00:34:45.940 --> 00:34:46.820
An art show?

00:34:47.380 --> 00:34:48.679
If he takes that painting

00:34:48.679 --> 00:34:49.719
Along with the others

00:34:50.920 --> 00:34:51.400
And puts it in the show...

00:34:52.519 --> 00:34:54.099
How can they be so disgusting?

00:34:54.519 --> 00:34:55.519
How could the Qi family

00:34:56.079 --> 00:34:57.739
Pull something like this?

00:34:58.119 --> 00:34:59.980
Just to earn a few lousy bucks,

00:35:00.619 --> 00:35:02.000
He's gonna drag our Xiaofang's dignity

00:35:02.000 --> 00:35:03.139
Through the mud.

00:35:03.699 --> 00:35:05.659
The Qi family is truly rotten to the core.

00:35:06.460 --> 00:35:08.280
They pull one dirty stunt after another.

00:35:08.860 --> 00:35:10.119
If only a fire would break out.

00:35:11.239 --> 00:35:12.699
We really oughta set their house ablaze.

00:35:35.940 --> 00:35:37.820
He must've painted Xiaofang!

00:35:43.619 --> 00:35:45.860
A nude painting! Everyone, tear it up!

00:36:01.119 --> 00:36:02.179
Murder!

00:36:02.340 --> 00:36:03.380
Help!

00:36:07.900 --> 00:36:09.360
He dared break into our house today.

00:36:09.900 --> 00:36:11.780
Tomorrow he'll kill Xiaowei!

00:36:12.800 --> 00:36:13.780
He's done time in prison.

00:36:14.739 --> 00:36:15.179
You tell me.

00:36:15.659 --> 00:36:16.940
Why did you have to provoke him?

00:36:16.940 --> 00:36:18.179
Look at what a wimp you are.

00:36:19.059 --> 00:36:19.599
How did I ever give birth

00:36:19.599 --> 00:36:20.639
To a good-for-nothing like you?

00:36:20.940 --> 00:36:21.940
Weren't you defending

00:36:21.940 --> 00:36:22.760
That Yang Fanhu?

00:36:23.659 --> 00:36:25.039
Didn't you say Xiaofang loves you?

00:36:25.860 --> 00:36:26.619
That whole Yang family

00:36:27.679 --> 00:36:28.940
Is a nest of tough nuts.

00:36:31.079 --> 00:36:32.320
Still won't listen to me!

00:36:33.199 --> 00:36:34.340
Go run after your Yang Xiaofang!

00:36:35.099 --> 00:36:36.079
Enough.

00:36:36.420 --> 00:36:37.699
Things have already come to this.

00:36:37.739 --> 00:36:38.699
What's the point of saying all that?

00:36:39.239 --> 00:36:40.960
Think of something. What do we do?

00:36:41.239 --> 00:36:42.539
Come up with a plan.

00:36:44.500 --> 00:36:46.400
They don't want to blow this up, right?

00:36:47.900 --> 00:36:49.219
Then we'll blow it up even bigger.

00:36:53.960 --> 00:36:54.460
No, Dad.

00:36:54.880 --> 00:36:55.280
No.

00:36:55.760 --> 00:36:56.219
No.

00:36:57.460 --> 00:36:57.840
What is it?

00:36:57.960 --> 00:36:59.019
We can't stir this up anymore.

00:36:59.380 --> 00:37:00.639
If we do, something terrible will happen.

00:37:01.039 --> 00:37:01.460
Dad, I'm begging you.

00:37:01.460 --> 00:37:02.679
Isn't this big enough already?

00:37:03.500 --> 00:37:04.300
Do as I say.

00:37:06.639 --> 00:37:07.300
Listen to your dad.

00:37:18.440 --> 00:37:20.519
Deng Erjin, I want to report a crime.

00:37:21.539 --> 00:37:22.239
What kind of case?

00:37:22.800 --> 00:37:24.380
Yang Fanhu, breaking and entering.

00:37:25.139 --> 00:37:25.719
Qi Deyao.

00:37:26.420 --> 00:37:27.460
Let me give you a lesson in the law.

00:37:28.099 --> 00:37:29.719
Slander carries legal consequences too.

00:37:30.000 --> 00:37:31.300
What kind of person is Fanhu?

00:37:31.440 --> 00:37:32.219
Would he steal from you?

00:37:32.599 --> 00:37:35.059
You snuck into the Qi house in the dead of night

00:37:35.639 --> 00:37:37.300
Just to take back this painting!

00:37:40.059 --> 00:37:41.380
That's my daughter!

00:37:41.960 --> 00:37:42.599
Do you have any idea

00:37:42.599 --> 00:37:43.940
How serious this is?

00:37:44.260 --> 00:37:45.400
We're clearly the ones in the right!

00:37:46.119 --> 00:37:46.579
And now,

00:37:47.179 --> 00:37:50.519
Qi Deyao's accusing you of breaking and entering.

00:37:50.900 --> 00:37:52.119
A painting was stolen from my house.

00:37:53.179 --> 00:37:54.219
What painting? Who painted it?

00:37:54.860 --> 00:37:55.260
Speak.

00:38:00.519 --> 00:38:02.000
You, what are you doing? Come here.

00:38:02.780 --> 00:38:03.599
Get in here!

00:38:04.980 --> 00:38:06.400
Tell them who painted it!

00:38:07.440 --> 00:38:09.440
Bro, you're something else.

00:38:09.960 --> 00:38:11.900
Didn't scare Qi Xiaowei to death, did you?

00:38:12.639 --> 00:38:13.719
That one shout last night

00:38:14.039 --> 00:38:15.559
Had every dog in the village barking.

00:38:16.559 --> 00:38:17.500
Coward.

00:38:22.579 --> 00:38:23.219
Speak. Who painted it?

00:38:24.480 --> 00:38:25.840
Who painted it? Say it!

00:38:29.800 --> 00:38:30.219
I did.

00:38:30.760 --> 00:38:31.699
You painted it?

00:38:32.980 --> 00:38:33.599
Qi Xiaowei,

00:38:34.119 --> 00:38:35.780
How much could your painting even be worth?

00:38:36.719 --> 00:38:37.800
Stop wasting police resources here.

00:38:39.380 --> 00:38:39.900
Deng Erjin!

00:38:40.860 --> 00:38:41.639
Watch how you talk!

00:38:42.019 --> 00:38:42.820
Whether that painting's valuable or not,

00:38:42.840 --> 00:38:43.820
That's for you to say?

00:38:44.699 --> 00:38:45.719
I'm reporting a crime.

00:38:46.059 --> 00:38:47.079
I didn't say I wouldn't take it.

00:38:47.079 --> 00:38:47.699
But you need evidence.

00:38:47.699 --> 00:38:48.280
Forget it, forget it.

00:38:48.280 --> 00:38:48.900
You have no proof.

00:38:48.900 --> 00:38:49.380
Shut up!

00:38:49.519 --> 00:38:51.659
You want to be called a rapist?

00:38:51.659 --> 00:38:52.500
You little brat!

00:38:55.579 --> 00:38:56.579
Are you taking this case or not?

00:38:57.239 --> 00:38:58.360
Are you taking it or not?

00:39:00.639 --> 00:39:01.079
Let's take a statement.

00:39:09.360 --> 00:39:10.280
Where do you think you're going?

00:39:10.699 --> 00:39:12.320
The Qi family's suing your dad.

00:39:14.480 --> 00:39:15.360
Don't worry.

00:39:15.579 --> 00:39:16.300
I'll work this out

00:39:16.300 --> 00:39:17.179
With Xiaowei.

00:39:17.820 --> 00:39:18.460
You're not going anywhere.

00:39:19.159 --> 00:39:20.480
You have to listen to me on this.

00:39:21.179 --> 00:39:22.599
Auntie's been through this.

00:39:22.800 --> 00:39:24.199
I've suffered this kind of loss before.

00:39:25.039 --> 00:39:25.579
Auntie.

00:39:26.000 --> 00:39:27.219
I can definitely sort this out

00:39:27.219 --> 00:39:27.940
With Xiaowei.

00:39:28.619 --> 00:39:29.699
He didn't rape me,

00:39:29.920 --> 00:39:31.460
And my dad didn't break in and steal.

00:39:31.840 --> 00:39:32.880
We're getting married,

00:39:32.880 --> 00:39:33.860
Not going to war.

00:39:34.460 --> 00:39:35.619
This IS war.

00:39:36.179 --> 00:39:37.099
It's no longer about

00:39:37.099 --> 00:39:38.880
You and Qi Xiaowei being lovey-dovey.

00:39:39.039 --> 00:39:40.000
It's not just between

00:39:40.000 --> 00:39:40.800
The two of you anymore.

00:39:41.000 --> 00:39:43.360
It's now a war between two families.

00:39:43.980 --> 00:39:44.380
Exactly.

00:39:45.179 --> 00:39:45.739
What's this?

00:39:45.920 --> 00:39:46.659
Is this a painting?

00:39:46.900 --> 00:39:47.900
This is a weapon.

00:39:47.940 --> 00:39:48.300
Right.

00:39:48.679 --> 00:39:49.599
What kind of man is Qi Deyao?

00:39:50.039 --> 00:39:51.460
You think he really wants to sue your dad?

00:39:51.719 --> 00:39:53.079
He just wants leverage

00:39:53.079 --> 00:39:54.019
To use it as a pretext.

00:39:54.420 --> 00:39:54.719
That's right.

00:39:54.719 --> 00:39:55.980
If we back down,

00:39:56.119 --> 00:39:57.860
The Qis will take advantage of the situation

00:39:58.000 --> 00:39:58.940
And be greedy for more.

00:39:59.719 --> 00:40:00.260
Us Yangs

00:40:00.780 --> 00:40:01.659
Won't take this loss.

00:40:01.780 --> 00:40:02.099
Right.

00:40:04.059 --> 00:40:04.760
Let him sue.

00:40:06.099 --> 00:40:06.699
Worst case,

00:40:07.820 --> 00:40:08.699
I'll go back inside again.

00:40:08.760 --> 00:40:09.780
What did you say?

00:40:09.840 --> 00:40:10.260
Brother.

00:40:10.480 --> 00:40:11.980
That's too reckless.

00:40:12.539 --> 00:40:13.179
Right now,

00:40:13.420 --> 00:40:14.579
You just stay home

00:40:14.739 --> 00:40:15.719
And behave yourself.

00:40:15.940 --> 00:40:16.619
Don't show your face.

00:40:17.199 --> 00:40:17.880
This matter,

00:40:18.320 --> 00:40:18.840
We'll handle it.

00:40:19.099 --> 00:40:19.460
Right.

00:40:21.219 --> 00:40:21.900
We'll handle it.

00:40:41.280 --> 00:40:42.059
Where's Yang Fanhu?

00:40:43.019 --> 00:40:43.800
Won't own up to what he did?

00:40:44.260 --> 00:40:45.099
Hiding, is he?

00:40:45.159 --> 00:40:45.760
My brother

00:40:46.360 --> 00:40:47.579
Is out serving our village.

00:40:47.960 --> 00:40:49.179
Protecting the mountains and forests.

00:40:49.460 --> 00:40:50.599
Cracking down on lawbreakers.

00:40:51.119 --> 00:40:52.119
Unlike some people

00:40:52.699 --> 00:40:54.679
Who sneak around doing shady things.

00:40:55.059 --> 00:40:56.860
Who's sneaking around, exactly?

00:40:57.500 --> 00:40:59.139
Yang Fanhu broke into our house

00:40:59.139 --> 00:41:00.519
In the middle of the night to steal!

00:41:01.039 --> 00:41:01.559
This right here!

00:41:02.179 --> 00:41:03.019
The whole village knows

00:41:03.019 --> 00:41:04.219
Our Xiaowei painted this.

00:41:04.340 --> 00:41:05.900
Learn some law, would you?

00:41:06.280 --> 00:41:06.860
My brother

00:41:07.019 --> 00:41:08.280
Wasn't breaking and entering.

00:41:08.940 --> 00:41:10.280
He was gathering evidence.

00:41:10.480 --> 00:41:12.079
This painting is the evidence.

00:41:12.559 --> 00:41:12.920
That's right.

00:41:13.500 --> 00:41:14.380
Qi Xiaowei used painting

00:41:14.400 --> 00:41:16.039
As an excuse to deceive Xiaofang.

00:41:16.719 --> 00:41:17.500
We're going to sue him!

00:41:18.659 --> 00:41:19.519
Sue what?

00:41:20.179 --> 00:41:20.519
This...

00:41:21.480 --> 00:41:23.340
Xiaofang clearly came onto him.

00:41:23.679 --> 00:41:25.320
What decent girl

00:41:25.559 --> 00:41:27.139
Strips naked to be painted?

00:41:27.199 --> 00:41:27.519
This...

00:41:27.659 --> 00:41:28.440
If you put it that way,

00:41:29.099 --> 00:41:30.579
We Qis have our pride too.

00:41:30.920 --> 00:41:32.159
Who'd dare marry a girl like that?

00:41:32.400 --> 00:41:32.880
Who'd dare?

00:41:33.239 --> 00:41:35.360
Our Xiaofang is the victim!

00:41:35.400 --> 00:41:36.079
Victim, my foot!

00:41:36.079 --> 00:41:36.539
Get your facts straight first.

00:41:36.539 --> 00:41:37.699
Qi Xiaowei

00:41:37.739 --> 00:41:38.860
Used painting as an excuse

00:41:39.099 --> 00:41:40.260
To do improper things.

00:41:40.619 --> 00:41:41.199
This painting

00:41:41.460 --> 00:41:42.139
Is the physical evidence.

00:41:42.500 --> 00:41:44.039
The baby in Xiaofang's belly

00:41:44.219 --> 00:41:45.280
Is the living proof.

00:41:45.360 --> 00:41:45.699
That's right.

00:41:45.780 --> 00:41:46.599
Okay, okay, okay.

00:41:46.900 --> 00:41:47.920
Everyone calm down.

00:41:48.139 --> 00:41:49.239
Please, sit down first.

00:41:50.179 --> 00:41:52.139
This is all about the two kids.

00:41:52.199 --> 00:41:53.340
Let's not make it so ugly.

00:41:53.880 --> 00:41:54.940
As for Yang Fanhu,

00:41:55.260 --> 00:41:56.159
I can vouch for him.

00:41:56.500 --> 00:41:57.480
He did it for the kids too.

00:41:57.659 --> 00:41:58.480
No ill intent.

00:41:59.340 --> 00:42:00.780
Miao Minzhi, who do you think you are?

00:42:00.800 --> 00:42:01.840
You dare to vouch for him?

00:42:02.260 --> 00:42:03.940
How much has Yang Fanyan sweet-talked you?

00:42:04.159 --> 00:42:05.559
Don't be unreasonable.

00:42:05.699 --> 00:42:06.940
Stop beating around the bush.

00:42:07.119 --> 00:42:07.739
Get to the point.

00:42:07.739 --> 00:42:08.599
You're taking sides!

00:42:08.639 --> 00:42:09.239
Stop!

00:42:11.679 --> 00:42:12.719
Get to the point.

00:42:17.139 --> 00:42:17.699
Xiaowei,

00:42:19.820 --> 00:42:20.780
Who leaked the painting?

00:42:25.219 --> 00:42:26.880
The whole village knows about it now.

00:42:27.219 --> 00:42:28.559
No point talking about that now, kid.

00:42:29.119 --> 00:42:29.480
Uncle,

00:42:29.480 --> 00:42:30.760
Xiaowei and I are in a relationship.

00:42:31.239 --> 00:42:32.639
We can paint whatever we want.

00:42:32.639 --> 00:42:33.880
It's our private business.

00:42:34.400 --> 00:42:36.079
Whoever, without our permission,

00:42:36.280 --> 00:42:37.820
Secretly photographed it and spread it,

00:42:37.820 --> 00:42:39.079
They're the ones breaking the law.

00:42:52.099 --> 00:42:53.340
Since everyone's already seen the painting,

00:42:53.340 --> 00:42:54.639
There's no point hiding it anymore.

00:42:56.480 --> 00:42:57.019
Oh my God!

00:42:58.440 --> 00:42:59.099
What are you doing?

00:43:06.599 --> 00:43:07.219
Qi Xiaowei,

00:43:11.079 --> 00:43:12.780
That's not me you painted at all!

00:43:13.559 --> 00:43:14.260
Then who is it?

00:43:16.460 --> 00:43:17.260
Qi Xiaowei!

00:43:23.480 --> 00:43:24.679
Their marriage

00:43:24.860 --> 00:43:27.260
Is being blocked by you parents.

00:43:27.340 --> 00:43:28.719
You two can't be in-laws,

00:43:29.260 --> 00:43:30.780
But don't hold the two kids back.

00:43:31.199 --> 00:43:32.559
Qi Xiaowei, look at me.

00:43:32.900 --> 00:43:34.139
Don't hide anything from me.

00:43:34.639 --> 00:43:35.940
Tell me whatever it is.

00:43:36.539 --> 00:43:38.079
Why won't you admit it?

00:43:38.679 --> 00:43:40.679
You enjoy being talked about behind your back?

00:43:41.039 --> 00:43:42.659
If you don't use this bride price thing

00:43:43.159 --> 00:43:44.780
To shut Yang Xiaofang down for good,

00:43:45.059 --> 00:43:46.639
Who knows what trouble she'll stir up later.

00:43:49.559 --> 00:43:49.900
This...

00:43:50.400 --> 00:43:51.460
Do you have any sincerity?

00:43:51.539 --> 00:43:53.300
Would a sincere person offer this little?

